long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly extract Eventbrite event detail data including image, eventId, paidStatus, title, description, locale, startTime, endTime, location, organizer, organizerUrl, eventUrl etc from the search result page to a Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Go to the eventbrite search result page.
2️⃣ Perform a search, click the "Start" button on extension popup.
3️⃣ Choose to download from the data scraping pop-up or the task list on extension.

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by eventbrite❗️🔒
